{"tid":2147602,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"加速滅絕師太 - 林夕","createTime":"2020-08-09T10:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T11:02:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de55dfd08e170a4a4b058f897849b5263f72a102","tid":2147602,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/KUFGQXD5VRCYTGOSBAGVOJXNWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FKUFGQXD5VRCYTGOSBAGVOJXNWE%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=260004de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FKUFGQXD5VRCYTGOSBAGVOJXNWE%2F&h=7c0dc05e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/KUFGQXD5VRCYTGOSBAGVOJXNWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n加速滅絕師太 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ItpOGiZ_vO_C_jScac4IE28B2Kg=/3969x2908/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DLAD5DUPFBH2XBO6MZB5SMTJ7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FItpOGiZ_vO_C_jScac4IE28B2Kg%3D%2F3969x2908%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDLAD5DUPFBH2XBO6MZB5SMTJ7M.jpg&h=b8b9379b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滅絕師太貿然宣布押後立會選舉一年，她沒有想到過一件事，抑或又想到過，而且正為有這效果而沾沾自喜呢？<br />\n<br />\n選舉要延期一年，同時亦即宣布，香港疫情在一年內都嚴重到生人勿近，旅遊、商貿、會議、展覽，外人別多作遐想。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n目前疫情當然嚴重到爆，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n千擔萬憂，。。。。。。以至於她一直傲然以對。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。鬼。金融不穩，脫鉤這種謠言傳遍街坊鄰里，資金不撤就有古怪。看看Citibank外面申請離岸戶口的人龍，問問市民何以有此舉動，舉一反三，外資又會有何舉措？你一個權力包羅宇宙的國安法，好幾個國際巨頭的數據中心，一個不留全都遷移到競爭國家去了，你還能色厲內荏多久？<br />\n<br />\n事關國際金融中心安危，我們的財政司司長又有何應對高見？人躲到哪裏去，要不要出來回應一下，川普說那些錢要回到紐約，讓紐約吊打當年紐倫港之中的香港國際金融中心啊。<br />\n<br />\n不用回了。這個上市交易所，早已在去國際化。看看市值一百大的上市公司名單，有多少是祖國企業，多少比例是國企，就一目了然。而這也不是一天兩天的事，趨勢早已形成，負責金融有司，自己心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n如今滅絕師太還要對外跟隨祖國戰狼外交口吻，對外變相宣布香港一年內處於疫埠狀態，師太果然同時無愧於加速滅絕師太之美名。"},{"pid":"6492519ff4b311cfc13a05e95069fe7de784a9f0","tid":2147602,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"入大直路 加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}